<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>Digital Legal Desk</title>
  <link rel="icon" href="assets/favicon/favicon.png" type="image/png">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Orbitron:wght@700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: 'Orbitron', sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: #f5f5f5;
    }

    header {
      background: #003366;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px 0;
    }

    header h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
    }

    header p {
      margin: 5px 0 0;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }

    .fixed-logo {
      position: fixed;
      top: 10px;
      left: 10px;
      width: 40px;
      height: 40px;
    }

    section {
      padding: 20px;
      max-width: 900px;
      margin: auto;
    }

    .service {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 10px;
      box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
      padding: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .service img {
      max-width: 80px;
      float: right;
    }

    footer {
      background: #003366;
      color: white;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 15px 0;
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      .service img {
        float: none;
        display: block;
        margin: 10px auto;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>

  <img src="assets/favicon/favicon.png" alt="Fixed Logo" class="fixed-logo">

  <header>
    <h1>Digital Legal Desk</h1>
    <p>Trusted Online Legal Solution</p>
  </header>

  <section>
    <div class="service">
      <h2>Legal Advice</h2>
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/619/619034.png" alt="Advice">
      <p>Get expert legal advice online from professionals. Your legal questions answered quickly and confidentially.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service">
      <h2>Document Drafting</h2>
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/3135/3135715.png" alt="Document">
      <p>We draft legal documents including agreements, notices, and affidavits tailored to your needs.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="service">
      <h2>Online Filing</h2>
      <img src="https://cdn-icons-png.flaticon.com/512/2921/2921822.png" alt="Online Filing">
      <p>Submit your legal forms and documents securely through our online portal and track updates easily.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <footer>
    &copy; 2025 Digital Legal Desk. All Rights Reserved.
  </footer>

</body>
</html>
